#

Bacon and Egg Pasta

25 min
$8.5
680 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

EggsGluten

Dietary Tags:

QuickEasyComfort Food

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Main CourseDinner

Tags:

PastaBaconComfort FoodQuick Meal

Description

A deliciously creamy pasta dish with crispy bacon and perfectly cooked eggs, ready in just 25 minutes!

Ingredients

  • pasta (spaghetti or fettuccine): 200g
  • bacon: 150g
  • eggs: 2
  • parmesan cheese: 50g
  • garlic (minced): 2 cloves
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • black pepper: to taste
  • salt: to taste
  • fresh parsley (chopped): for garnish
